udflare.com.\n```\nThese are **Cloudflare's authoritative name servers** that control all DNS records for this domain.\n\n### **SOA Record (Start of Authority)**\n```\nPrimary NS: bart.ns.cloudflare.com.\nAdmin Email: dns.cloudflare.com.\nSerial: 2392992790\nRefresh: 10000s\nRetry: 2400s\nExpire: 604800s\nMin TTL: 1800s\n```\nContains administrative information about the DNS zone, including the primary nameserver, contact email, and various timing parameters for DNS updates.\n\n## Summary\nThe domain **datawizz.ai** is:\n- Hosted behind **Cloudflare** (CDN + DDoS protection)\n- Using **Google Workspace** for email\n- Properly configured with SPF for email authentication\n- Has both IPv4 and IPv6 support"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1135,"cache_read_input_tokens":15275,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1135,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":760,"service_tier":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CWs1pCSyHdppC2yQckNAN","type":"assistant","uuid":"79aa733f-b03e-400a-aad1-00a612fdf017","timestamp":"2026-01-06T23:45:53.923Z"}
